Ask us stuff on reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/kurzgesagt/comments/f4qmuz/ask_us_questions_get_answers_today_or_in_a_future/

For years, you have been asking us how we make our videos. So lets finally talk about it! From research, writing the script, illustrating, to animating, narrating and composing music, a Kurzgesagt video takes roughly 1.200 hours to produce! 

OUR CHANNELS

German Channel: https://kgs.link/youtubeDE by FUNK
Spanish Channel: https://kgs.link/youtubeES by WIX
